{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT is not only a tool that individuals can use; I n d u s t r i a l M a n a g e m e n t & D a t a S y s t e m s",
    "organizations at a larger scale may also improve their processes by efficiently integrating ChatGPT with the existing internal knowledge base.",
    "The rich and diversified knowledge base of ChatGPT integration will enhance the decision quality to the next level compared to the earlier decisions made merely through the internal knowledge base.",
    "Explicit knowledge is \"know what\" knowledge about work practices in organizations described in formal language using print or electronic document format (Smith, 2001).",
    "In a conventional knowledge management system, explicit knowledge is managed by keeping a complete record of organizational documents and an efficient retrieval system (Gamble, 2020)."
  ]
}